snippet.title: Best VGM 860 - Ogre Battle 64 - Decisive
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo 64
Ogre Battle 64 (2000)
Decisive
Hitoshi Sakimoto, Hayato Matsuo & Masaharu Iwata
